He suggested this place.

1358
01:25:26,960 --> 01:25:28,160
Mr. Kaso...

1359
01:25:28,400 --> 01:25:30,760
Well...

1360
01:25:30,960 --> 01:25:32,520
We're starting the project soon.

1361
01:25:32,600 --> 01:25:35,040
