- No! No!
- What are you doing!

1388
01:26:38,160 --> 01:26:40,800
- No! No!
- He's shooting a video!

1389
01:26:40,880 --> 01:26:43,320
- We gotta go. We'll go viral!
- But where do we go?

1390
01:26:43,400 --> 01:26:45,000
- We must get out.
- How?

