01:26:45,120 --> 01:26:47,560
- Jomin, help us out.
- You must know this place!

1392
01:26:47,640 --> 01:26:49,400
- Look there!
- Look upstairs!

1393
01:26:53,400 --> 01:26:55,720
- Call up Panda!
- I'm on it.

