01:27:00,200 --> 01:27:02,160
- Anything?
- No!

1397
01:27:02,240 --> 01:27:03,960
- There's no signal here.
- What!

1398
01:27:04,440 --> 01:27:07,040
- Stop it!
- Just keep looking.

1399
01:27:10,200 --> 01:27:11,400
Hey!

