01:27:14,920 --> 01:27:16,200
Bhaski, no! You'll get hurt.

1401
01:27:16,280 --> 01:27:17,880
There's no exit!

1402
01:27:27,800 --> 01:27:28,920
Bhaski!

1403
01:27:30,400 --> 01:27:32,720
Hey! Did you hear that?

1404
