Bhaski...

1441
01:30:11,520 --> 01:30:12,600
Jomin!

1442
01:30:15,600 --> 01:30:18,600
This is your last chance to do Kung-Fu.

1443
01:30:18,960 --> 01:30:20,480
Bhaski!

1444
01:30:27,600 --> 01:30:29,880
Shoo! Shoo! Get away!

1445
01:30:30,000 --> 01:30:33,680
